title: Sizzling Savings! $500 Rent Credit!**Wexford Apts- 1 BR Apartments**
posting_body: ['***RENT SPECIAL: $400 RENT CREDIT + ADDTIONAL $100 IF YOU APPLY THE SAME DAY AS YOUR SHOWING!', '*** CALL TODAY FOR MORE DETAILS', 'WEXFORD COMMONS APARTMENTS', '208 W. 62nd Street, Minneapolis, MN 55419', 'Available JULY/AUGUST', 'Starting at $950/month', 'Wexford Commons Apartments offers 1 bedroom apartment homes for rent in South Minneapolis, bordering Richfield and close to the Hub Shopping Center.', ' It is close  to many restaurants, shops, recreational opportunities, the bus line and much more.', 'Easy freeway access to downtown Minneapolis, Edina, Bloomington, and Mall of America.', '1 BR - Deposit starting at $400', '$40 Application Fee per Adult', 'MANAGEMENT PAYS FOR ALL UTILITIES, Except Electric', 'SPECTACULAR OFFICE STAFF', 'AMAZING 24 HOURS MAINTENANCE STAFF', 'Cats Accepted with the Following Restrictions:', 'Cats - $250 non-refundable pet fee, $30 monthly pet rent, a limit of 2 cats per apartment, and must be spayed/neutered.', 'Call today and let our professional staff give you a personal tour of the community.', '*Prices and availability are subject to change at any time.']
